data.name: AM2R11SuccessfulDescription
data.value: The zip is a valid copy of AM2R_11.

data.name: AM2R11MissingExeDescription
data.value: The "AM2R.exe" file is missing from the zip, or it is invalid. Please ensure you have a correct AM2R_11 copy.

data.name: AM2R11MissingD3DDescription
data.value: The "D3DX9_43.dll" file is missing from the zip, or it is invalid. Please ensure you have a correct AM2R_11 copy.

data.name: AM2R11MissingDataDescription
data.value: The "data.win" file is missing from the zip, or it is invalid. Please ensure you have a correct AM2R_11 copy.

data.name: AM2R11SubfolderDescription
data.value: The game is located in a subfolder, which is unsupported. This can be fixed by extracting the zip into a folder, navigating into there, selecting all files and then creating a new zip from it.
